Rosie,

With all due respect for your best intentions, are you claiming that
messages posted to this list become the property of antenneX? That
seems to be the case since you can't prosecute anyone for theft (or
even "Thieft") of something that isn't yours.

The lengthy "Welcome" message I received when I subscribed gave no
indication that antenneX would own my posts and I suspect that other
members would be surprised and perhaps offended by this notion. Please
clarify this for us.

